There are just a few things they need to do.<br>
<br>
1.  Level's 1 through 50.  Excellent leave them be.<br>
<br>
2. Lower resists for Wizards 50+ alot.  The most insulting thing to see for a wizard is, Your spell has been resisted.<br>
As it stands right now we have only a tiny bit better resists, but we need lower resist period.<br>
<br>
3. In the high end level game, in xp groups, and on velious uber mobs, we do not go the distance.  (58+ lvl)  Add a level 60 wizard spell.. 100 mana 600 damage 4 to 6 second cast unresistable. <br>
This one spell would balance the class and make us needed in velious and xp groups.  We could go the distance again.  Normally a wiz in an xp group nukes 2 times per fight 1 bub of blue mana per say = appox 1500 damage per fight.  With this spell we could nuke approx 5 times in the same fight and do approx 3k damage to the mob for the same mana.  <br>
<br>
We do not need a 2k damage 100 mana unresistable spell, that would over power us.  We do need the spell here it is once again.<br>
<br>
Level 60 (bought on a vendor)<br>
Inner magic strike<br>
Mana: 100<br>
Damage: 600<br>
Casting time: 4 seconds<br>
Special: Unresistable (No component)<br>
Recast delay: 0<br>
<br>
One spell and I bet like this and you would never hear a wizard gripe again.  It enhances our group damage by double for the same mana, and makes us wanted on &quot;magic resitant mobs&quot;<br>
<br>
Roclar Lorestar<br>
